00:42:11,960 --> 00:42:13,920
TELEPON UMUM POLISI

854
00:42:32,160 --> 00:42:33,000
BERIKUTNYA

855
00:42:33,080 --> 00:42:35,600
- <i>Ini</i> Bridgerton.
